org.zyp.cn8583.impl
类 cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen

java.lang.Object
  org.zyp.cn8583.impl.cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen
所有已实现的接口：
cnSystemTraceNumGenerator
public class cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen
extends java.lang.Object
implements cnSystemTraceNumGenerator

这是一个中国版的8583格式标准的类，初始代码来源于类SimpleTraceGenerator。 取系统跟踪号的方法已经同步。 Simple implementation of a cnSystemTraceNumGenerator with an internal number that is increased in memory but is not stored anywhere.

作者：
zyplanke

构造方法详细信息

cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen

public cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen(int initialValue)
Creates a new instance that will use the specified initial value. This means the first nextTrace() call will return this number.

参数：
initialValue - a number between 1 and 999999.
抛出：
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the number is less than 1 or greater than 999999.

指定者：
接口 cnSystemTraceNumGenerator 中的 getLastTrace

nextTrace

public int nextTrace()
Returns the next number in the sequence. This method is synchronized, because the counter is incremented in memory only.

指定者：
接口 cnSystemTraceNumGenerator 中的 nextTrace
